"some frightening points. It seems that alien craft will actually grow faster "
"as they become larger and more powerful, and there's no doubt that, if they "
"can build these Harvesters, they can build bigger and nastier UFOs. We "
"should try to adapt the alien antimatter technologies to our own "
"interceptors as soon as possible so that we can get on an even footing with "
"the aliens now and will be able to stand up to more dangerous threats in the "
"future.\n"
"\n"
"--Cdr. Navarre\n"
