"metal and part plastic polymer. It functions as a memory alloy, "
"'remembering' at least two assigned shapes, shrinking into a more compact "
"form when cold but automatically stretching out and assuming a more "
"comfortable flying shape once it heats up. It's far stronger and tougher "
"than anything we've ever known. More research is definitely required.\n"
